item.title: By: Eric Greenwood
item.dc:creator: Eric Greenwood
item.description: you are insane. the new 90210 is so awful it's not even funny. the girls are not hot (excepting silver). and the writing is atrocious. abominable show. gossip girl is far seedier and thus - by default - the winner. sometimes i truly wonder about your taste.
